com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component

Class ComponentValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.component.ComponentValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class ComponentValue
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity class modeling the data base Table ComponentsValue. The purpose of this table is to saves values of the SelectOneMenu web component, when the user create that type component. the class contains queries that extract information from the table, columns and relation with other tables.
